{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Portfolio/blog/3/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Tinnia Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4eb79ad9-0412-593c-a429-9d77d4890c3c","excerpt":"Gatsby + React Font 바꾸기  - local에서 폰트 바꾸기 1️⃣ 폰트 저장할 폴더 만들기  - src에 fonts 폴더 만들기 2️⃣ 원하는 폰트를 골라 다운로드하기  - 눈누에서 다운받음 3️⃣ style.css에서 수정 4️⃣ 추가 : 수정이 안 될 때  - src…","html":"<h4>Gatsby + React Font 바꾸기</h4>\n<p> - local에서 폰트 바꾸기</p>\n<h5>1️⃣ 폰트 저장할 폴더 만들기</h5>\n<p> - src에 fonts 폴더 만들기</p>\n<h5>2️⃣ 원하는 폰트를 골라 다운로드하기</h5>\n<p> - <a href=\"https://noonnu.cc/\">눈누</a>에서 다운받음</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shnolinenumbers\"><pre class=\"language-shnolinenumbers\"><code class=\"language-shnolinenumbers\"># src/fonts/\nTmoneyRoundWindExtraBold.ttf\nTmoneyRoundWindRegular.ttf</code></pre></div>\n<h5>3️⃣ style.css에서 수정</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* src/style.css */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">--fontFamily-sans</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'TmoneyRoundWindExtraBold'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">--fontFamily-serif</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'TmoneyRoundWindRegular'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">--font-body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--fontFamily-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">--font-heading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--fontFamily-sans<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h5>4️⃣ 추가 : 수정이 안 될 때</h5>\n<p> - src에 fonts.css 만들기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* src/fonts.css */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@font-face</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'TmoneyRoundWindExtraBold'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'./fonts/TmoneyRoundWindExtraBold.ttf'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'woff'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@font-face</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'TmoneyRoundWindRegular'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'./fonts/TmoneyRoundWindRegular.ttf'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'woff'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h5>5️⃣ 추가 : gatsby-browser.js 수정</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-browser.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./src/fonts.css\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<br />\n<hr />\n<h4>Gatsby + React Icon 넣기</h4>\n<h5>1️⃣ npm 설치</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm install react-icons --save</code></pre></div>\n<h5>2️⃣ 사용하기</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> FaBeer <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-icons/fa'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Question</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h3<span class=\"token operator\">></span> Lets go <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FaBeer <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h3<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Blog] 03. Font 바꾸기 & Icon 넣기","category":"Portfolio","date":"2020/Nov/06","description":"[Gatsby + React] Font 바꾸기 & Icon 넣기"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/portfolio/blog/2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Blog] 02. 페이지 만들기","path":"/Portfolio/blog/2/"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/programmers/체육복/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Programmers/Python] 체육복","path":"/Algorithm/programmers/42862/"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4eb79ad9-0412-593c-a429-9d77d4890c3c","previousPostId":"9b1affb3-06f3-512a-ba5a-c7edabd0bcc5","nextPostId":"fb8e6887-78fd-5008-8c5d-89a6edae4640"}},"staticQueryHashes":["642825376"]}